msgid ""
"This allows tasks to be disabled for specific statuses such as \"Draft\" or "
"\"Published."
msgstr ""
"Eyi gba iṣẹ́ laaye lati jẹ́ aláìlera fún àwọn ipo pataki gẹ́gẹ́ bí \"Ìkàwé\" "
"tàbí \"Tí a tẹ̀jáde.\""

msgid "This allows users to duplicate existing checklist tasks."
msgstr "Èyí gba àwọn olumulo laaye láti da àwọn iṣẹ́ àtòkọ tí ó wà lọ́wọ́ pọ̀."

msgid ""
"Add a Checklists column to the Posts screen showing how many requirements "
"are complete."
msgstr ""
"Fi kolomu Checklists kun si iboju Posts ti o nfihan bi ọpọlọpọ ibeere ti "
"pari."

msgid ""
"This allows tasks to be disabled for posts with specific taxonomy terms. Go "
"to the \"Post Types\" tab to choose the terms."
msgstr ""
"Èyí gba àwọn iṣẹ́ laaye láti jẹ́ kó ma ṣiṣẹ́ fún àwọn ìpò pẹ̀lú àwọn ọrọ̀ "
"taxonimy pàtó. Lọ sí taabu \"Iru Ìpò\" láti yan àwọn ọrọ̀ náà."

msgid ""
"This will display a warning icon in the \"Checklists\" box if requirements "
"are incomplete."
msgstr ""
"Eyi yóò fi aami ikilọ hàn nínú apoti \"Àwọn Atokọ\" tí awọn ibeere kò pé."

msgid ""
"This will highlight Gutenberg blocks that fail block-specific checklist "
"tasks."
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"When enabled, all PublishPress Checklists data will be deleted if the plugin "
"is uninstalled."
msgstr ""
"Nigbati o ba ti mu ṣiṣẹ, gbogbo data PublishPress Checklists yoo parẹ ti a "
"ba yọ akopọ naa kuro."

msgid "This will show \"Exclude User Roles\" options."
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"Disabling the \"Status\" option is recommended because it can be used to "
"avoid using the Checklists requirements."
msgstr ""
"Dákẹ́ àṣayan \"Ipo\" ni a ṣe iṣeduro nitori pe a le lo lati yago fun lilo "
"awọn ibeere Checklists."

msgid ""
"This will disable \"Quick Edit\" for all users except those with the "
"\"manage_options\" capability."
msgstr ""
"Eyi yóò pa \"Ṣatunkọ Kánkán\" fun gbogbo awọn olumulo ayafi fun awọn ti o ni "
"agbara \"manage_options\"."

msgid ""
"This will disable the \"Publish\" button when checklist requirements are not "
"met."
msgstr "Eyi yóò pa bọtini \"Tẹ̀jáde\" run nigbati awọn ibeere atokọ ko ba pade."

msgid "Enter your API Key to use OpenAI prompts in checklist tasks."
msgstr "Tẹ bọtini API rẹ lati lo awọn ibeere OpenAI ninu awọn iṣẹ akọsilẹ."

